T1  - Living With Multiple Paradigms the Case of Paradigm Interplay in Organizational Culture Studies
AU  - Schultz, Majken
AU  - Hatch, Mary Jo
Y1  - 1996/04/01
PY  - 1996
DA  - 1996/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1996.9605060221
